00:00:00.133 --> 00:00:02.102
 Way2Go saves money and less stress and is more environmentally friendly 

00:00:02.970 --> 00:00:05.305
 If you use an electric wheelchair or a general wheelchair 

00:00:05.372 --> 00:00:08.208
 You have a lot of choices in transportation. 

00:00:08.275 --> 00:00:09.275
 It is a good way to travel by TCAT bus. 

00:00:12.679 --> 00:00:16.116
 All TCAT buses are equipped with active ramps or lifting devices 

00:00:16.216 --> 00:00:18.252
 And has a dedicated area for a stable wheelchair 

00:00:18.852 --> 00:00:23.690
 In fact, if you are disabled and enjoy social supplementary welfare social welfare disability insurance 

00:00:23.757 --> 00:00:25.392
 Or disabled veterans' welfare 

00:00:25.626 --> 00:00:27.661
 You can enjoy half price on bus 

00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:30.264
 You can also follow the itinerary 

00:00:30.330 --> 00:00:31.565
 Choose to use the Gadabout car 

00:00:31.798 --> 00:00:33.834
 Or you can combine two services 

00:00:33.901 --> 00:00:38.138
 Complete your partial journey by bus and use the Gadabout to complete another part of the itinerary 

00:00:40.174 --> 00:00:43.076
 This can greatly improve the scope of your travel 

00:00:44.111 --> 00:00:49.449
 Way2Go bus basics video contains information about finding a bus 

00:00:49.550 --> 00:00:50.551
 Plan to travel 

00:00:50.651 --> 00:00:54.087
 And purchasing and using the ticket card or T card content 

00:00:54.555 --> 00:00:57.357
 In this video we will show you 

00:00:57.424 --> 00:01:01.161
 How convenient is it to use a wheelchair or an electric wheelchair to get on the bus and travel 

00:01:01.728 --> 00:01:04.631
 When the bus driver stops at the bus stop and sees you 

00:01:04.765 --> 00:01:06.700
 They put down the active ramp or lifting device 

00:01:09.169 --> 00:01:11.171
 Get on the ramp 

00:01:11.471 --> 00:01:14.875
 If the ramp looks too steep or has other equipment problems 

00:01:14.942 --> 00:01:16.910
 Please let the driver know your needs 

00:01:16.977 --> 00:01:18.979
 - Sorry, I am late~ Hello. 

00:01:19.213 --> 00:01:20.247
 Are you ok? 

00:01:20.314 --> 00:01:21.582
 After getting in the car 

00:01:21.782 --> 00:01:24.284
 Use cash or T card to buy a ticket 

00:01:24.418 --> 00:01:27.454
 You can use the T card to swipe the card at the front of the bus or hand the cash directly to the driver. 

00:01:27.855 --> 00:01:31.491
 If you need a driver, you will let other passengers change seats. 

00:01:32.226 --> 00:01:36.096
 The wheelchair-only area is located at the front of the bus. 

00:01:36.196 --> 00:01:38.165
 The driver will fix the wheelchair 

00:01:40.367 --> 00:01:43.003
 Don't forget to tell the driver where you got off at the stop 

00:01:43.070 --> 00:01:45.606
 You can easily enjoy your journey. 

00:01:48.675 --> 00:01:52.412
 When the bus drives to the station you are going to, the driver will release your wheelchair from the fixture. 

00:01:52.846 --> 00:01:55.415
 Let the wheelchair drive to the active ramp and get off 

00:02:01.588 --> 00:02:04.525
 If there is no bus to the destination you are going to 

00:02:04.691 --> 00:02:06.360
 Or if you can't go 

00:02:06.426 --> 00:02:08.896
 Public station to go 

00:02:09.062 --> 00:02:12.065
 Consider using a Gadabout car to complete all or part of your trip. 

00:02:13.033 --> 00:02:16.003
 The Kings County Gadabout car is dedicated to living in Tomkins County. 

00:02:16.136 --> 00:02:19.806
 Travel services for people with disabilities or the elderly 

00:02:20.240 --> 00:02:24.278
 You can find it on the TCAT website at TCATbus.com under the ADA tab. 

00:02:24.411 --> 00:02:29.183
 View Gadabout information about ADA's auxiliary passenger services 

00:02:30.884 --> 00:02:34.021
 By taking the bus and using the Gadabout car 

00:02:34.087 --> 00:02:36.290
 You can travel to Kings County. 

00:02:36.356 --> 00:02:38.292
 Some places that the bus cannot reach 

00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:43.764
 It is very simple to use a wheelchair or an electric wheelchair for a public bus. 

00:02:44.064 --> 00:02:47.367
 TCAT drivers can make your travel more convenient 

00:02:47.534 --> 00:02:49.269
 So that you can go anywhere 

